"2 1/2 pounds baby red potatoes, cut into 1-inch cubes","2 tablespoons apple cider vinegar","1 tablespoon olive oil","1/2 cup whole buttermilk","1/4 cup reduced-fat sour cream","1/4 cup reduced-fat mayonnaise with olive oil","1 tablespoon Dijon mustard","2  carrots, grated","1/2 cup chopped celery","1/2 cup sliced radishes","1/2 cup steamed, cut fresh green beans","1/4 cup finely chopped fresh parsley","1 tablespoon lemon zest","1  garlic clove, minced","  Sea salt and freshly ground pepper to taste"